trans-unit.source: Contains information about the workflow instance associated with a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Contém informações sobre a instância de fluxo de trabalho associada a um <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Esta classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] The runtime tracking infrastructure passes a TrackingParameters object in when it calls <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.GetTrackingChannel%2A> on a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]A infraestrutura de controlo do tempo de execução transmite um objeto de TrackingParameters no quando chama <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.GetTrackingChannel%2A>no <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.GetTrackingChannel%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can use these parameters in your tracking service to associate tracking data received on the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> with a specific workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Pode utilizar estes parâmetros no seu serviço de controlo para associar dados de controlo recebidos a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>com uma instância de fluxo de trabalho específico.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>
